    <conbody>
        <p>Convert DOCX, PDF, FrameMaker, HTML, Markdown, JATS, DocBook, and custom XML
            into standards‑compliant DITA‑XML.</p>
        <p><b>What You Get</b></p>
        <ul id="ul_rzq_ppv_c3c">
            <li>Structure‑aware parsing</li>
            <li>Style &amp; hierarchy preservation</li>
            <li>Block‑level difference validation</li>
            <li>Schema‑validated output</li>
        </ul>
        <p><xref href="https://met-r.io/contact" format="html" scope="external">Request a Migration
                Assessment</xref></p>
        <section id="section_ktt_cqv_c3c">
            <title><b>Govern Without Git Complexity</b></title>
            <p><ph keyref="product_name"/> introduces <b>Git‑light workflows</b> designed
                for content teams - not developers.</p>
            <ul id="ul_lhr_kqv_c3c">
